<div id="front"></div>
<div class="wrapper medium">
  <h2 class="c light-gray" style="margin-top: 0;">
    Welcome to Hana's Tradewind Cottage
  </h2>

  <p>
    As you follow the private drive through the tropical flower garden to our
    secluded Tradewinds Cottage, you will
    discover the Hawaii that you came to see.
  </p>

  <p>
    Surrounded by exotic flowers and tropical fruit trees, our two bedroom, one bath cottage has cable TV, DVD and CD
    stereo. There is a gas cook top, refrigerator and microwave oven in the newly remodeled kitchen with a propane
    barbeque outside on the covered deck. Wireless Internet access is available on the property.
  </p>

  <p>
    The cottage has a queen size bed, two twin beds and a queen size sleeper sofa. You'll enjoy the splendor of the
    slopes of Haleakala while relaxing in your private hot tub or cooking your favorite island-style feast on the
    barbeque under your covered lanai.
  </p>
</div>
<%= section_header('Reservations') %>

<div class="wrapper medium-minor mb20">
  <p class="medium">
    Planning a trip to the east side of Maui? Be sure to book your stay with us as early as possible.
    We are usually booked months in advance.
  </p>

  <h4>Rates</h4>
  <ul class="pad medium-minor">
    <li>Nightly rate for <%= text_field_tag(:people_count, 2, class: 'instep', maxlength: 2) %> people
      <span>+13.5% tax</span> = <span class="bold" id="rate_result">$198.63</span>
    </li>
    <li>The cottage can accommodate a <b>maximum of 4 guests.</b></li>
    <li><b>Note:</b> There is a charge of $25 per night for each additional person.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Reservation Policies</h4>

  <ul class="pad medium-minor">
    <li>
      <b>Minimum stay:</b> We have a two night minimum stay for all reservations made more than a week in advance,
      except when there is an open night “sandwiched” between two existing reservations. We are happy to accept one
      night stays 7 days in advance. There will be a $25 cleaning fee for a one night reservation for two people and
      a $35 cleaning fee for three or four people who stay for only one night.
    </li>

    <li>
      <b>Deposits:</b> A 25% deposit is required to reserve the cottage and the balance is due 30 days in advance.
    </li>

    <li style="margin-top: -15px;">
      <b>Payment:</b> We accept Visa, MasterCard, American Express and Discover.
      <span><%= image_tag(asset_path('visa_mastercard_american_express_discover.png'), style: 'position: relative;top: 13px;') %></span>
    </li>

    <li>
      <b>Check-in:</b> <br/>
      Check-in time is 3:00 p.m. <br/>
      Check-out time is 11:00 a.m.
    </li>

    <li>
      <b>Cancellation:</b>
      We will refund your deposit less a 10% cancellation fee if you notify us
      <span class="medium bold">30 days prior to you arrival</span>.
      Cancellations within 30 days of your arrival will be refunded only for the nights we are able to re-book the
      accommodations minus a 10% service fee.
      <p>
        If you check out prior to your scheduled check out date we will refund only for the nights we are able to
        re-book
        the accommodations minus a 10% service fee.
      </p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <b>Laundry facilities</b> are available free of charge for guests staying 5 or more nights.
    </li>

    <li>
      <b>Special Terms:</b> <br/>
      Rates and policies are subject to change.<br/>
      To provide a smoke free environment for our guests, smoking is only allowed outside. <br/>
      No pets are allowed at the cottage.<br/>

      <p><a href="#contact">Make a reservation inquiry.</a></p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Availability</h4>
  <% unless Rails.env.development? %>
      <iframe src="https://www.homeawayconnect.com/calendar.aspx?propertyid=51970&culturename=en-US&mode=1" style="width:100%;height: 990px;"></iframe>
  <% end %>
</div>
